# 'Married', 'Together' 제외 나머지 값 리스트

# 재범주화
data['Marital_Status'] = data['Marital_Status'].replace(['Married', 'Together'], 'Relationship').replace(list(set_diff), 'Single')

2-2. Histogram¶

In [90]:
fig, axs = plt.subplots(ncols = 2, nrows = 2, figsize = (15, 10))
sns.set_style('white')
for i in range(0, 2):
  for j in range(0, 2):
    axs[i, j].grid(True, axis = 'x')
sns.set_style("whitegrid", {'axes.grid' : False})
sns.histplot(data['Wines'], ax = axs[0,0], color = 'pink', edgecolor = 'black', kde = False).set(xlabel = 'Wine')
sns.histplot(data['Fruits'], ax = axs[0,1], color = 'skyblue',  edgecolor = 'black', kde = False).set(xlabel = 'Fruit')
sns.histplot(data['MeatProducts'], ax = axs[1,0], color = 'purple', edgecolor = 'black', kde = False).set(xlabel = 'Meat')
sns.histplot(data['SweetProducts'], ax = axs[1,1], edgecolor = 'black', color = 'orange', kde = False).set(xlabel = 'Sweets')
plt.suptitle('Items bought by Customers', fontsize = 30)
Out[90]:
